    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Single-headed circular frame drums of the Near East, North Africa, and as far east as Malaysia, usually with metal jingles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
